-size: 9pt; color: black; font-family: Arial\">（1）负责客户接待及协议谈判签署工作；&nbsp;<br />\r\n（2）根据公司业务流程对学生的学习状况做出分析与诊断，制定辅导计划与方案。&nbsp;<br />\r\n（3）负责与家长沟通协调工作。&nbsp;<br />\r\n（4）负责教学点学生的心理辅导，帮助其养成良好的学习兴趣和学习习惯。热诚，强烈企图 心，勇于挑战高业绩。</span></p>\r\n<p><font face=\"宋体\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">联系人：丁老师</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"宋体\">联系电话：</font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\">025-86524689</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"宋体\">电子邮箱：</font></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: black; font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial\"><a href=\"mailto:jsnjtlg@163.com\"><span style=\"color: black\">jsnjtlg@163.com</span></a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size: 9pt; font-family: Arial\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','','',0,1,'2011-05-06 23:10:54'),(68,0,18,'电话邀约员','桃李阁教育','','<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"宋体\">因公司业务扩展，急聘电话邀约员<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>名，一旦录用，公司将提供完善的福利保障，良好的发展空间</font></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial\"><font face=\"宋体\">。<span style=\"font-family: Arial\"> </span></font></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 13.5pt; color: black; font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-f