eithr of hate doing <br />\r\n199 no +</span>名词<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n200 not anymore = no more </span>再也不<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip; eg: He didn\'t cry any more He cried no more </span>他再也不哭<span lang=\"EN-US\">201 not&hellip; (</span>形 、副）<span lang=\"EN-US\">at all eg: He\'s not tall at all she doesn\'t junp far at all <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n202 not&hellip;at all </span>一点都不<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n203 not&hellip;either </span>表否定，也不<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : I don\'t japanse either I don\'t have sister, either </span>我也没有姐姐<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n204 not&hellip;until </span>直到<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>才<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip; <br />\r\neg: I didn\'t sleep until my mother came back The child didn\'t stop crying until I give her sugar <br />\r\n205 offer / provide sb with sth </span>给某人提供<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n206 offer sb sth ( offer sth to sb </span>提供什么东西给某人<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : I offer you water (I offer water to you </span>我给你提供水<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n207 on one\'s way to&hellip; </span>在谁去那的路上<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n208 on the one hand </span>一方面<span lang=\"EN-US\"> on the other hand </span>另一方面<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n209 on the phone = over the phone </span>用电话交谈<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n210 on time </span>准时<span lang=\"EN-US\"> in time </span>及时<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n211 one day </span>＝<span lang=\"EN-US\">some day </span>＝<span lang=\"EN-US\">someday </span>一天，有一天<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n212 one of +</span>可数名词的复数形式<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n213 one to another </span>一个到另一个<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n214 over and over agin </span>一遍又一遍的<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : He cleaned the floor over and over agin <br />\r\n215 part-time job </span>兼职工作<span lang=\"EN-US\"> fall-time job </span>全职工作<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n216 pay for&hellip; </span>付<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>钱<span lang=\"EN-US\"> pay the bill </span>开钱，付钱<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n217 please +do <br />\r\n218 please help yourself <br />\r\n219 pleased with sb <br />\r\n220 pool into = pore into <br />\r\n221 practice +doing </span>练习做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n222 prefer sth to sth </span>相对<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>更喜欢<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip; eg : I prefer physics to chemisty </span>在物理和化学中，我更喜欢物理<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nprefer doing to sth </span>更喜欢去做<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;</span>不愿意去做<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip; eg: He prefers riding a bike to diving </span>他更喜欢骑自行车，不开小车<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nprefer to do sth rather than do sth </span>宁愿做<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;</span>也不愿<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\neg: My unde prefers to buy a now car rather than repaiv the used one </span>我叔叔更喜欢买新的车，也不去修旧车<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nprefer sb not to do sth </span>更愿意<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip; eg: I prefer her not to come </span>我不喜欢她不来<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n223 pretend to do sth </span>装着去做什么<span lang=\"EN-US\"> pretend that </span>从句<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\neg : The two cheats pretended to be working very hard </span>这两个骗子装着努力工作<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nHe pretended that he did not know the answer </span>他装着不知道答案<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n224 rather&hellip;than </span>宁可<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>也不<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip; <br />\r\neg : I would rather be a doctor than a teacher </span>我愿肯当医生，也不当老师<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nHe likes dogs rather than cats </span>他喜欢狗，不喜欢猫<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n225 regard&hellip;as </span>把<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>当作<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip; <br />\r\neg: Please give my best regards to your family </span>请带我向你的家人我最好的问候<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nI regard you as my friend </span>我把你当作我的朋友<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nHe shows little regard for others </span>他不爱关心别人<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n226 remid sb about sth </span>提醒某人什么事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> remid sb to do sth </span>提醒某人做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\neg : he remids me about cooking (he remids me to cook </span>他提醒我做饭<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n227 remid sb of sth </span>使某人想起什么<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\neg : the pictures remind me of my school days </span>这照片使我想起了我的学校<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nthe words that (which) the teacher talke to remind me of my mother <br />\r\n228 return sth to sb </span>还什么东西给某人<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n229 say to oneself </span>对自己说<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n230 say to sb </span>对某人说<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n231 sb spend somemoney on sth </span>花了多少钱在某事上<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n232 sb spend sometime with sb </span>花了多少时间陪谁<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n233 sb spend sometime(in) doing sth </span>花了多少时间做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n234 sb with sb +is sb and sb +are <br />\r\n235 see sb do </span>看见某人做过某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> see sb doing </span>看见某人正在做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n236 seem to do/be +adj </span>显得怎么样<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : You seem to be tired You seem to be happy <br />\r\n237 send +sb sth </span>送给某人某物<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n238 send&hellip;to&hellip;</span>把什么寄到哪里去？<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n239 shock </span>使<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>震惊<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : Oh , It\'s only you ! You give me a shock </span>啊，是你呀！吓我一跳<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n240 show sb sth </span>向某人展示某物<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : I show her the book. <br />\r\n241 show sb sth = show sth to sb </span>拿什么东西给某人看<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg: Show me your pen Show your pen to me <br />\r\n242 show sth to sb </span>向某人展示某物<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : I show the book to her. <br />\r\n243 some&hellip;others&hellip; </span>一些<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>另一些<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip; <br />\r\n244 start&hellip;with&hellip; </span>从<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>开始<span lang=\"EN-US\"> begin&hellip;with&hellip; </span>从<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;</span>开始<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n245 stay away from </span>远离<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip; <br />\r\neg : We\'re told to stay away from the animals whe visiting the zoo </span>当我们参观<span lang=\"EN-US\">zoo </span>时，我们要远离动物<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\nIf you want to lose weight you\'d better stay auay from the sweet food </span>徒工你想减肥，你最好远离甜食<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n246 stop doing </span>停下正在做的事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n247 stop sb from doing sth </span>阻止某人做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n248 stop sb(from) doing </span>阻止某人做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n249 stop to do </span>停下正在做的事去做下一件事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n250 such +</span>名 这样 ，这种<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n251 suit sb </span>适合某人<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n252 surprise sb </span>使某人惊奇<span lang=\"EN-US\"> to one\'s surprise </span>令某人惊奇<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n253 take classes </span>上课<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n254 take sb to </span>把某人带去<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : I take you to the hospital <br />\r\n255 take walks = take a walk </span>＝<span lang=\"EN-US\"> go for a walk </span>散步<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n256 ①talk to </span>对谁说<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : I talk to you ② talk with </span>和谁说<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : I talk with him <br />\r\n③ talk of </span>谈到<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : we talked of you ④ talk about </span>谈论关于<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip; <br />\r\n257 talk with sb </span>和某人说话<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n258 teach sb sth </span>教某人做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n259 tell sb do sth </span>告诉某人做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n260 tell sb sth tell sb that </span>丛句<span lang=\"EN-US\"> tell sb not to do sth tell a story <br />\r\n261 tell sb sth </span>告诉某人某事<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n262 tell sb to do sth </span>告诉某人做什么<span lang=\"EN-US\"> tell sb not to do sth </span>告诉某人不要做什么<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n263 tell&hellip;from&hellip; <br />\r\n264 thank you for +doing <br />\r\n265 the same +</span>名词<span lang=\"EN-US\">(doing)+as&hellip;&hellip; <br />\r\n266 the same&hellip;(</span>名<span lang=\"EN-US\">)&hellip;as as&hellip;(adj adv)&hellip;as </span>相同<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n267 the way to do sth </span>＝<span lang=\"EN-US\"> the way of doing st</span>做某方面 的方法<span lang=\"EN-US\">the way to +</span>地方 去哪的路<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\ne g :Do you know the way to learn English Do you know the way of learning English <br />\r\n268 the way to&hellip;</span>（地点） 到哪的<span lang=\"EN-US\">269 too&hellip;to&hellip; </span>太怎样而不能<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;&hellip;adj +enough to </span>足够<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip;</span>能<span lang=\"EN-US\">&hellip; so&hellip;that +</span>丛句<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\neg: He is too young to go to school = He is so young that he can\'t go to school <br />\r\nHe is old enough to go to school </span>＝<span lang=\"EN-US\"> He is so old that he can go to school <br />\r\n270 transalte &hellip;&hellip;into&hellip;&hellip; </span>把什么翻译成什么<span lang=\"EN-US\"> eg : Trasalte English into chinese <br />\r\n271 travel with sb</span>和某人去旅游<span lang=\"EN-US\">272 try one\'s best to do sth</span>尽某人最大的努力去做某事<span lang=\"EN-US\">eg: I will try my best to learn English well 273 try to do sth </span>想干什么，但没成功<span lang=\"EN-US\"> try doing sth </span>想干什么，已经做过了<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\neg </span>：<span lang=\"EN-US\">He tried to climb </span>他想爬上去，但没成功<span lang=\"EN-US\"> He tried climbing </span>他想爬上去，已经做过了<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n274 try&hellip;</span>试衣服<span lang=\"EN-US\"> have a try </span>试一下<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 275 turn down </span>开小<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &larr;&rarr; turn up </span>开大<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n276 turn off </span>关上<span lang=\"EN-US\"> &larr;&rarr; turn on </span>打开<span lang=\"EN-US\"> open </span>拆开<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 277 upside down </span>倒着<span lang=\"EN-US\"> <br />\r\n278 visit to&hellip; </span>参观某个地方<span lang=\"EN-US\"> 279 wait for sb </span>等某人<span lang=\"EN-US\"><br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break\" />\r\n<br style=\"mso-special-character: line-break\" />\r\n</span></span></p>','','初中英语语法总结',0,1,'2011-07-27 11:21:11'),(125,0,20,'语文答题公式','桃李阁教育','桃李阁教育','<p>（一）某句话在文中的作用：&nbsp; <br />\r\n1、文首：开篇点题；渲染气氛（散文），埋下伏笔（记叙类文章），设置悬念（小说，但上海不会考），为下文作辅垫；总领下文；&nbsp; <br />\r\n2、文中：承上启下；总领下文；总结上文；&nbsp; <br />\r\n3、文末：点明中心（散文）；深化主题（记叙类文章文章）；照应开头（议论文、记叙类文章文、小说）&nbsp;<br />\r\n（二）修辞手法的作用：<br />\r\n（1）它本身的作用；（2）结合句子语境。&nbsp; <br />\r\n1、比喻、拟人：生动形象；&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 答题格式：生动形象地写出了＋对象＋特性。&nbsp; <br />\r\n2、排比：有气势、加强语气、一气呵成等；&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 答题格式：强调了＋对象＋特性&nbsp; <br />\r\n3；设问：引起读者注意和思考；&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 答题格式：引起读者对＋对象＋特性的注意和思考&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 反问：强调，加强语气等；<br />\r\n4、对比：强调了&hellip;&hellip;突出了&hellip;&hellip;&nbsp; <br />\r\n5、反复：强调了&hellip;&hellip;加强语气&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n（三）句子含义的解答：&nbsp; <br />\r\n这样的题目，句子中往往有一个词语或短语用了比喻、对比、借代、象征等表现方法。答题时，把它们所指的对象揭示出来，再疏通句子，就可以了。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n（四）某句话中某个词换成另一个行吗？为什么？<br />\r\n动词：不行。因为该词准确生动具体地写出了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\r\n形容词：不行。因为该词生动形象地描写了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\r\n副词（如都，大都，非常只有等）：不行。因为该词准确地说明了&hellip;&hellip;的情况（表程度，表限制，表时间，表范围等），换了后就变成&hellip;&hellip;，与事实不符。<br />\r\n（五）一句话中某两三个词的顺序能否调换？为什么？&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n不能。因为：<br />\r\n（1）与人们认识事物的（由浅入深、由表入里、由现象到本质）规律不一致。<br />\r\n（2）该词与上文是一一对应的关系。<br />\r\n（3）这些词是递进关系，环环相扣，不能互换。&nbsp;<br />\r\n（六）段意的概括归纳&nbsp; <br />\r\n1．记叙类文章：回答清楚（什么时间、什么地点）什么人做什么事。&nbsp; <br />\r\n格式：（时间＋地点）＋人＋事。&nbsp; <br />\r\n2．说明类文章：回答清楚说明对象是什么，它的特点是什么。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 格式：说明（介绍）＋说明对象＋说明内容（特点）<br />\r\n3．议论类文章：回答清楚议论的问题是什么，作者观点怎样。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 格式：用什么论证方法证明了（论证了）＋论点&nbsp;<br />\r\n（七）表达技巧在古代诗歌鉴赏中占有重要位置，表现手法诸如用典、烘托、渲染、铺陈、比兴、托物寄情、情景交融、借景抒情、动静结合、虚实结合、委婉含蓄、对比手法、讽喻手法、象征法、双关法等等。诗中常用的修辞方法有夸张、排比、对偶、比喻、借代、比拟、设问、反问、反复等。分析诗歌语言常用的术语有：准确、生动、形象、凝练、精辟、简洁、明快、清新、新奇、优美、绚丽、含蓄、质朴、自然等。复习时要系统归纳各种表达技巧，储备相关知识。首先要弄清这些表达技巧的特点和作用，再结合具体诗歌进行仔细体味、辨析。&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n至于评价诗歌的思想内容和作者的观点态度，则包括总结作品的主旨，分析作品所反映的社会现实，指出其积极意义或局限性等。总之，鉴赏古代诗词，第一步，把握诗词内容，可以从以下几方面入手：1细读标题和注释；2分析意象；3品味意境；4联系作者。第二步，弄清技巧：1把握形象特点；2辨析表达技巧；3说明表达作用。第三步，评价内容观点：1概括主旨；2联系背景；3分清主次；4全面评价。<br />\r\n答题时，要特别注意以下几点：一是紧扣要求，不可泛泛而谈；二是要点要齐全，要多角度思考；三是推敲用语，力求用语准确、简明、规范。&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n易混术语区分<br />\r\n（一）&ldquo;方式、手法&rdquo;的区分<br />\r\n艺术手法，又叫表达技巧，包括：<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ①表达方式 ：记叙、描写、抒情、议论、说明。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ②表现手法 ：起兴、联想、烘托、抑扬、照应、正侧、象征、对照、由实入虚、虚实结合、运用典故、直抒胸臆、借景抒情、寓情于景、情景交融、托物言志、借古讽今、化动为静、动静结合、以小见大、开门见山。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ③修辞 ：比喻、借代、夸张、对偶、对比、比拟、排比、设问、反问、引用、反语、反复。<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n（二）&ldquo;情&rdquo;、&ldquo;景&rdquo;关系区别<br />\r\n借景抒情、寓情于景、情景交融都是诗人把要表达的感情通过景物表达出来。&ldquo;借景抒情&rdquo;表达感情比较直接，读完诗歌后的感受是见&ldquo;情&rdquo;不见&ldquo;景 &rdquo;；&ldquo;寓情于景&rdquo;、&ldquo;情景交融&rdquo;。表达感情时正面不着一字，读完诗歌后的感受是见&ldquo;景&rdquo;不见&ldquo;情&rdquo;，但是仔细分析后却发现诗人的感情全部寓于眼前的自然景色之中，一切景语皆情语。<br />\r\n（三）描写的角度<br />\r\n常见的角度有：形、声、色、态、味。&ldquo;形&rdquo;、&ldquo;色&rdquo;是视觉角度；&ldquo;声&rdquo;是听觉角度；&ldquo;态&rdquo;分为动态和静态；&ldquo;味&rdquo;是触觉角度。答题举例（06浦东新区模拟）回答1：同意。文章以&ldquo;山格&rdquo;为题，以拟人化的手法铺写了众多山的不同性情，赋予其以人的灵性：无论是南方的山灵秀不失狂野，还是北方的山健壮而不失妩媚，抑或是西部的山尊严而沉默&hellip;&hellip;总之，作者在对不同地域山的不同风格的描述中笔意纵横，令人饱览山之情味，行文大气而稳重。回答2：同意。首先，运用了大量拟人、比喻等修辞格，把山所表现出来的形态赋予丰富的人格性情；其次选材大气，描摹了南方、北方、西部山的个性，给读者以全面的感悟；最后又以山与人之关系升华作结，拓展了思考空间：大气尽显其中矣。就上海高考而言，它的理念是为学生服务的，是为学生升入高校服务的，而不是站在学生的对立面、设立难题，为难学生，它会为学生提供了舞台和机会，所出的题应该能够解答，但必须是有道理、有准备、有基础的。</p>','','语文答题公式',0,1,'2013-08-07 10:21:15'),(126,0,12,'送给桃李阁教育胡老师的一封感谢信','','','<p>尊敬的校长：<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 您好！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 写这封信，是要感谢桃李阁教育及胡老师。感谢他对孩子的关怀，感谢他对孩子的帮助，感谢他为学生们所做的一切，虽然只有短短的不到三个月的时间。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有人说，师恩如山。高山仰止，当更催后来人奋发不已。正所谓&ldquo;新竹高于旧竹枝，全凭老干扶持&rdquo;。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  孩子的点滴进步、些许成绩，全都凝聚着他辛勤的汗水。我们不会忘记他对孩子语重心长的开导和鼓励，&hellip;&hellip;这些点 点滴滴，也深深地印在了孩子的心里。所以，不管何时何地，无论天涯海角，我们和孩子都将由衷地感谢您&mdash;&mdash;敬爱的胡老师！我们的孩子永远是需要您启蒙的学 生！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 也许老师已经忘记了调皮的学生惹您生的气，已经忘记了您为学生的学习操的心，但我们无法忘记，您为年少的她鼓的掌、加的油。您用目光指引她，您用话语安慰她，无论是失意还是快乐，您那用心发生的光芒将永远伴随着她。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们两个都是普通工人，无权无势，更没有什么背景，但我们有一颗感恩的心。老师，您为什么一无所求呢？因为您心中装的是您的学生们，甚至爱她们都要超过了爱自己的孩子。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 您的无私奉献，都深深地镌刻在学生及家长的心里。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 我们还要感谢李老师、章老师，感谢他们在孩子成长过程中，给予孩子的帮助和教诲，感谢他们为孩子所做的一切！<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 正因为教师队伍中有了他们，老师&mdash;&mdash;人类灵魂的工程师，有着大海般丰富，蓝天一样深湛内涵的称谓，将永远让我们铭记。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 感谢桃李阁教育，感谢给予孩子帮助的各位老师。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 此致<br />\r\n&nbsp; 敬礼</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 初三班一名学生家长&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2011年8月5日</p>','','',0,1,'2011-08-07 19:20:43');
INSERT INTO `g_news` VALUES (127,0,12,'南京桃李阁教育初高中周末补习班/南京新街口秋季辅导班','桃李阁教育','桃李阁教育','<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 南京桃李阁教育是一家个性化课外辅导专业机构。南京桃李阁教育凭借着一流的师资队伍、专业的服务团队、先进的教育辅导模式、独特有效的教育方法和完善的管理模式，不断整合优秀的教育资源，为学生营造快乐的学习环境和先进的教育平台，为学生提供全方位的个性化教育服务。</p>\r\n<p>　　南京桃李阁教育专注于学生的学习能力培养和学校课程的同步辅导，为每一个学生量身定制最佳的学习方案，改善学习方法，激发学生们的智力潜能和学习兴趣，培养学生的自学能力。</p>\r\n<p>　　开设科目：小学 初中、高中各科<br />\r\n　　教学模式：一对一个性化教学 精品小班</p>\r\n<p>　　师资力量：由省、市重点名校教学经验丰富的一线教师授课。</p>\r\n<p>　　上课方式:</p>\r\n<p>　　(1)平时班　周一到周五　08:00　&mdash;&mdash;　21:00 <br />\r\n　　(2)周末班　周六、周日　08:00　&mdash;&mdash;　21：00</p>\r\n<p>　　一对一：　根据学生的时间进行安排，合理灵活</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;上课时间：&nbsp;&nbsp;2课时/次&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 60分钟/课时</p>\r\n<p>　　教学管理：专业学习管理师全程跟踪学生的学习过程，并就学生的学习、生活上的问题与家长进行及时沟通、定期回访。</p>\r\n<p>　　中高考冲刺班：以新课改为方向、以考纲为标准，科学总结学习方法和规律，紧扣高考考点、重点、难点，提供全面、系统的学习，深入讲解常见错误、典型例题、解题技巧。同时 强调深度思维的培养、激发学生的潜能，让学生对知识点融会贯通并迅速提高应试能力和解题能力，为中高考冲刺提供强有力的保障。</p>\r\n<p>艺术+文化冲刺班：量身制定学习计划，对历年高考考题,典型试题,进行详细评析,反复练笔,在最短的时间内,最大程度的发掘学生潜能,由各学科老师制定相应的学习计划。</p>','','文化课辅导',0,1,'2013-08-07 10:20:53'),(128,0,12,'2013年春季周末班招生简章','','桃李阁教育','<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px\">&nbsp; 桃李阁教育一对一,vip小班辅导是由南京各<span style=\"color: #0000ff\">中小学名校特高级教师</span>主讲，几年来不断得到家长和学生的好评，很多孩子以优异的成绩考入树人国际,金中,南外等名校,欢迎加入到桃李阁的大家庭中来!由我们来助你成功,实现梦想!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">单科小班</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> :</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">适应学生:单科成绩不是很理想，希望在一段时间内养成良好的学习习惯，提高学习成绩,</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">根据学生的成绩制定个性学习方案，确定学习目标</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> .</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">辅导时间：8：00&mdash;21:00</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">提优班</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> :</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">适应学生:学习水平处于中等及中等以上，希望迈向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">尖子生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">的学生</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> ,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">教学形式：名师组织教学，引导学习兴趣，改进学习方法，注重解题思路.</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">辅导时间：8：00&mdash;21:00</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">小升初冲刺班：</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">适应学生：立志在小升初最后一年取得突破性进展，进入知名学府的学生。由名师组织教学，围绕考试大纲，科学的组织复习冲刺，讲解考试题型、解题思路、应试技巧等 。辅导时间：<font face=\"宋体\">8：00&mdash;21:00</font><br />\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">中高考冲刺班:</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">适应学生</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">：面临中高考，平时没有尽力学习的应届生，立志在中高考最后一年取得突破性进展，进入知名学府的学生</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">教学形式：由名师组织教学，围绕考试大纲，科学的组织复习冲刺，讲解考试题型、解题思路、应试技巧等</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> ,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">辅导时间：8：00&mdash;21:00</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">小高考冲刺班:</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">适应学生;基础薄弱，想保</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">C</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">争</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">得同学；</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">基础一般，想保</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">B</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">争</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">A</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">的同学</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> ,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">由名师组织教学，围绕考试大纲，科学的组织复习冲刺，讲解考试题型、解题思路、应试技巧等</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> ,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">辅导时间：8：00&mdash;21:00<br />\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">艺术生文化课补习班：</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">适应学生：专业成绩过关，但文化成绩不好的学生。</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">周一<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">~周日<strong><font face=\"宋体\">8__21:00</font></strong></span>，由非常有辅导艺术考生文化课经验的老师授课，文化高考通过率99%。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">寒暑假优惠班</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> ：</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px\"><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">适应学生，希望在寒、暑假时间内衔接课程，在开学时成绩领先的学生</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> 。</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">一线教师对新课程的知识点、难点、要点进行有效衔接</span><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\"> ，</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">辅导时间：周一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">~</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Tahoma; mso-hansi-font-family: Tahoma; mso-bidi-font-family: Tahoma\">周日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">8:00~21</span></span></span><span style=\"color: #ff0000\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Tahoma; color: black; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.5pt\">:00</span></font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">普通班:</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;五年级：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 上午：&nbsp;数学、英语&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;下午：&nbsp;语文(1310&mdash;14:40)<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;六年级：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 上午：&nbsp;数学、英语&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;下午：&nbsp;语文(13:10&mdash;14:40)&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;初一年级：&nbsp;&nbsp;上午：&nbsp;数学、英语&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;下午：&nbsp;语文(13:10&mdash;14:40)&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;初二年级：&nbsp;&nbsp;上午：&nbsp;数学、物理&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;下午：&nbsp;英语、&nbsp;语文&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;初三年级：&nbsp;&nbsp;上午：&nbsp;数学、英语&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;下午：&nbsp;物理、&nbsp;化学<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;高一年级：&nbsp;&nbsp;上午：&nbsp;数学、英语&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;下午：&nbsp;物理、&nbsp;化学&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;高二年级：&nbsp;&nbsp;上午：&nbsp;数学、英语&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;下午：&nbsp;物理、&nbsp;化学&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;高三年级：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 下午：&nbsp;数学、英语&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;一、 日程安排<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp