e=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">2.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">将（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）句据换一种说法 。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></u></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">3.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">将<span lang=\"EN-US\">(3)</span>画线的词组译成中文。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></u></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">4.What does a frog look like when he is young?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 27pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></u></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">5.What is the frog going to eat?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></u></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">B<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">Each part of your body has a job to do. All the parts work together to help each other. The heart sends blood to every part of the body.The blood gets oxygen</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">（氧气）<span lang=\"EN-US\">in the lungs(</span>肺<span lang=\"EN-US\">)</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\">Blood carries food and oxygen all over the body.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">The brain gets food and oxygen through the flood.Food and oxygen help the brain work. The brain tells all the parts what to do.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>All the parts work together to keep you alive and healthy.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span>Your body works for you. You must take care of your body so it can do its job. There are things you can do to help your body stay strong and healthy. You can exercise, drink water, eat good foods, and rest.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span>Eating and drinking give your body energy. Exercising and resting help keep your body strong .When you do good things for your body, you are more likely to stay healthy. It is important to take care of your body.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 21pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">( </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">每题<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>分<span lang=\"EN-US\">)<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">1.What is the story most about?<u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">A. The school<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>B. Your stomach.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>C. Your home.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>D. Your body.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">2. What is the main idea of the second paragraph?<u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">A. The body needs lots of exercise<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">B. The heart is the most important organ<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">C. The brain is the most important organ<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">D.The brain tells the body part what to do.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">3.What is good for you to drink?<u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">A.Coke<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>B.Water<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>C.Juice<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>D.Beer<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">4.What will probably happen if you take care of your body?<u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">A.You will never get sick.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>B. You willgrow up to be very tall.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">C.Your body will stop making oxygen. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">D.Your body will stay healthy and strong.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">5.Why should you eat good food?<u><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></u><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">A.It keeps you from being hungry. B. Eating gives your body energy.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">C.Food is grown by farmers.<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">D.Eating only one kind of food can make you sick.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 42pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 335.15pt; mso-char-indent-count: 3.5; mso-para-margin-left: 31.92gd\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\">C<o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: 12pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 1.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">Five adults </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">（成人）<span lang=\"EN-US\">and six children were swimming at Mawgan Porth beach near Newquay On Sunday 2 August when hidden tides pulled them out of their depth. Thankfully there were four lifeguards (</span>救生员<span lang=\"EN-US\">) on the beach, who were able to get to the group and save them.<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Toby, 12, said,</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">&ldquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">There probably would have been a couple of people <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">drowning </span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">（淹死） <span lang=\"EN-US\">if the lifeguards weren</span>&rsquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">t there.</span>&rdquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">The children had been<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span>swimming where the Flags said they were allowed to, but the current<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">（水流）<span lang=\"EN-US\">still caught hold of them.Jack,14, said, </span>&ldquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">I<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Wasn</span>&rsquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">t panicking,<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span>but I was worried about drifting</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">（漂流）<span lang=\"EN-US\"> away. I<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>didn</span>&rsquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">t know how far <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">I would go before the current ended. It</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">&rsquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">s<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>more dangerous thinking about<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp;</span>it now than it was at the time. At the time you don</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">&rsquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\">t know what is <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">happening.</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">&rdquo;<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -336pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 336pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes\">&nbsp; </span>Later the family went back to the beach to say thanks to the <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">lifeguards.They say They are going to put them forward for a bravery award.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -337.3pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt 337.3pt; mso-char-indent-count: -28.0\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">( </span></b><b st','','试卷',0,1,'2012-12-21 21:03:17');
